Rialto%20Bridge%2C%20one%20of%20Venice's%20top%20tourist%20sites%2C%20was%20not%20very%20busy%20when%20I%20visited.%3Cp%3EKelsey%20Vlamis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22770831c2-e107-4d9d-914e-ceed431f4e4a%5C%22%3EGo%20in%20the%20offseason%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20know%20all%20those%20shots%20you've%20seen%20of%20massive%20crowds%20near%20Venice's%20Rialto%20Bridge%20or%20St.%20Mark's%20Basilica%3F%20They%20all%20have%20something%20in%20common%3A%20they%20were%20taken%20during%20the%20busy%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Venice%2C%20that's%20generally%20considered%20April%20through%20October%2C%20with%20each%20month%20drawing%20well%20over%20half%20a%20million%20visitors%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20city.%20July%2C%20the%20busiest%20month%2C%20and%20August%20both%20drew%20more%20than%20600%2C000%20visitors.%20November%20to%20March%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20is%20considered%20the%20%26quot%3Bslow%26quot%3B%20season%2C%20drawing%20less%20than%20400%2C000%20visitors%20a%20month%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESustainable%20tourism%20experts%20have%20previously%20told%20me%20that%20a%20key%20driver%20of%20overtourism%20is%20not%20the%20total%20visitor%20numbers%20but%20that%20people%20often%20want%20to%20visit%20the%20exact%20same%20places%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20evident%20as%20I%20traveled%20through%20Venice%2C%20experiencing%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20crowd%20sizes%20that%20I%20had%20braced%20myself%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20visited%20a%20TikTok-famous%20bookstore%20that%20online%20reviewers%20said%20they%20waited%20an%20hour%20to%20get%20into%20and%20that%20there%20was%20not%20enough%20crowd%20control.%20But%20when%20I%20got%20there%20I%20simply%20wandered%20in%2C%20looked%20at%20the%20books%2C%20noticed%20some%20tourists%20taking%20selfies%2C%20and%20then%20moved%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20a%20last-minute%20lunch%20reservation%20at%20a%20beloved%20local%20restaurant%20that