20avoid.%20But%20when%20we%20walked%20by%20and%20saw%20there%20was%20plenty%20of%20open%20seating%2C%20inside%20and%20outside%2C%20we%20walked%20right%20in%2C%20sat%20down%2C%20and%20enjoyed%20a%20fancy%20coffee%20in%20a%20gorgeous%2C%20old-school%20caf%C3%A9%20without%20any%20of%20the%20crowd-induced%20chaos%20I%20had%20been%20warned%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20happened%20time%20and%20time%20again%20in%20Venice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERestaurants%20right%20along%20the%20Grand%20Canal%20in%20the%20most%20touristy%20areas%20seemed%20to%20always%20have%20seats%20available.%20The%20longest%20line%20I%20saw%20was%20probably%20for%20a%20gelato%20shop%20that's%20beloved%20on%20TikTok%2C%20Suso%2C%20and%20even%20that%20looked%20to%20be%20about%20a%2010-minute%20wait.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20offseason%20months%20may%20not%20have%20the%20best%20weather%2C%20but%20visiting%20during%20a%20shoulder%20season%20month%20like%20March%20felt%20like%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds.%20It%20was%20warm%20enough%20but%20not%20hot%2C%20requiring%20only%20a%20jacket%20and%20sometimes%20not%20even%20needing%20it%2C%20and%20we%20only%20experienced%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20drizzling%20rain.%20Personally%2C%20I%20would%20take%20that%20weather%20any%20day%20over%20the%20sweltering%20heat%20of%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Caffe%20Florian%20interior%20and%20a%20coffee.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fdb116a466d2b74ab3271c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20were%20plenty%20of%20open%20tables%20inside%20and%20outside%20at%20Caffe%20Florian.%3Cp%3EKelsey%20Vlamis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cf2255a3-d61a-49bd-a60b-d78c0afb881d%5C%22%3EStay%20in%20a%20residential%20neighborhood%20and%20let%20yourself%20wander%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Venice%20is%20made%20up%20of%20over%20a%20hundred%20islands%2C%20the%20main%20island%2C%20or%20historic%20center%2C%20is%20about%202%20square%20miles%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20exactly%20big%20enough%20to%20totally%20escape%20the%20tourists%2C%20which%20I've%20personally%20found%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20easier%20in%20big%2C%20sprawling%20cities%20like%20Rome%20or%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20choosing%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20the%20most%20touristy%20neighborhoods%20goes%20a%20long%20way%20in%20insulating%20you%20from%20the%20crowds.%20San%20Marco%20is%20the%20most%20popular%20neighborhood%20for%20tourists%20to%20stay%20in%20Venice%2C%20and%20it%20has%20the%20souvenir%20shops%20to%20prove%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20choosing%20somewhere%20closer%20to%20the%20main%20sites%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20stay%20in%20Cannaregio%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20residential%20districts%20of%20Venice's%20historic%20center%2C%20which%20only%20has%20about%2050%2C000%20permanent%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECannaregio%20was%20a%20lot%20quieter%20and%20had%20a%20more%20authentic%20feel%20than%20the%20more%20popular%20areas%20of%20Venice%2C%20but%20it%20was%20still%20not%20too%20far%20to%20walk%20to%20the%20main%20sites.%20The%20district%20had%20a%20seemingly%20endless%20number%20of%20quiet%20paths%20and%20canals%20to%20explore%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20take%20in%20the%20beauty%20of%20Venice%20without%20another%20soul%20in%20sight.%20We%20visited%20restaurants%20and%20bars%20that%20were%20full%20of%20locals%2C%20as%20well%20as%20tourists.%20We%20saw%20groups%20of%20local%20preteens%20sitting%20on%20the%20canals%20and%20small%20kids%20in%20soccer%20uniforms%20walking%20home%20with%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20genuinely%20and%20pleasantly%20surprised%20to%20see%20real%20glimpses%20of%20local%20life%20so%20close%20to%20the%20overly%20touristy%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Restaurant%20with%20outdoor%20seating%20on%20Grand%20Canal%20with%20open%20tables%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fdb0b7c6ad288d147e2428%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERestaurants%20with%20outdoor%20seating%20along%20the%20Grand%20Canal%20in%20the%20most%20touristy%20areas%20had%20plenty%20of%20open%20tables.%3Cp%3EKelsey%20Vlamis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef36f702-9a06-41c2-9425-17a3712e6372%5C%22%3EVisit%20another%20island%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20about%20four%20days%20to%20explore%20Venice%2C%20a%20city%20where%20most%20people%20don't%20even%20spend%20the%20night%2C%20and%20those%20who%20do%20spend%20an%20average%20of%20just%20over%20two%2C%20according%20to%20city%20data.%20But%20staying%20longer%20encouraged%20us%20to%20venture%20even%20further%20out%20of%20the%20historic%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20took%20a%20ferry%20%E2%80%94%20basically%2C%20Venice's%20equivalent%20of%20a%20public%20bus%20%E2%80%94%20to%20Murano%2C%20a%20small%20island%20that%20is%20famous%20for%20its%20glassmaking%20and%20that%20essentially%20feels%20like%20a%20quieter%20and%20smaller%20version%20of%20the%20main%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20it%20was%20only%20about%2010%20minutes%20by%20boat%20from%20the%20historic%20center%2C%20Murano%20was%20much%20quieter%20than%20Venice%2C%20making%20it%20even%20easier%20to%20wander%20without%20having%20to%20worry%20about%20overcrowding.%20It%20felt%20almost%20like%20a%20little%20getaway%20from%20the%20hustle%20and%20bustle%20of%20the%20main%20island%2C%20and%20sipping%20Aperol%20on%20the%20canal%20was%20just%20so%20much%20chiller%20than%20a%20comparable%20experience%20in%20the%20historic%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20more%20remote%20islands%20you%20can%20visit%20via%20the%20public%20water%20buses%2C%20like%20Burano%2C%20a%20tiny%20fishing%20village%20with%20rows%20of%20colorful%20homes%2C%20and%20Torcello%2C%20the%20historic%20island%20where%20Venice%20began%20with%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20residents%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1743a11-7c5e-4da5-9f87-5101a6ba031b%5C%22%3EManage%20your%20expectations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVenice%20surpassed%20my%20expectations%20and%20I%20ended%20up%20enjoying%20it%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20I%20anticipated.%20If%20you%20travel%20to%20Venice%20expecting%20to%20find%20quaint%20images%20of%20authentic%2C%20untouched%2C%20historic%20Venetian%20and%20Italian%20life%2C%20you%20may%20be%20disappointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20you'll%20likely%20see%20why%20it%20draws%20so%20many%20people%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20in%20the%20first%20place%20if%20you%20can%20manage%20your%20expectations%2C%20take%20some%20of%20these%20tips%2C%20and%20keep%20in%20mind%20you%20are%20visiting%20a%20place%20for%20which%20tourism%20has%20been%20a%20significant%20part%20of%20its%20economy%20since%20the%20end%20of%20the%2018th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-avoid-crowds-visiting-venice-overtourism-off-season-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744681490000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fdb1a4a466d2b74ab32727%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-avoid-crowds-visiting-venice-overtourism-off-season-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Venice%20famously%20struggles%20with%20overtourism%2C%20but%20I%20did%20three%20key%20things%20that%20helped%20me%20avoid%20crowds%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20time%20of%20year%20I%20chose%20to%20visit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40businessinsider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-avoid-crowds-visiting-venice-overtourism-off-season-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alamo%20Drafthouse%20Strike%20Ends%20With%20All%20Laid%20Off%20Staffers%20to%20Be%20Rehired%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published