es%20has%20worked%20for%20clients%20including%20Booz%20Allen%20Hamilton%20and%20security%20contractors%20that%20work%20with%20the%20State%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20move%20comes%20just%20over%20a%20month%20after%20Trump%20signed%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-big-law-fight-firms-legal-dilemma-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20described%20Perkins%20Coie%20as%20a%20security%20threat%2C%20suspended%20the%20security%20clearances%20of%20its%20personnel%2C%20and%20required%20that%20federal%20contractors%20disclose%20whether%20they%20work%20with%20the%20law%20firm.%20A%20few%20days%20later%2C%20Perkins%20convinced%20a%20judge%20to%20pause%20the%20order%2C%20but%20it%20said%20key%20clients%20had%20already%20told%20the%20firm%20to%20stand%20down%2C%20and%20it%20worried%20about%20losing%20their%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECanizares%20was%20the%20vice-chair%20of%20the%20government%20contracts%20team%20at%20Perkins%20and%20will%20be%20the%20cohead%20of%20Vinson's%20government%20contracts%20group.%20He%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20his%20move%20to%20Vinson%20was%20in%20the%20works%20for%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20months%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20was%20laying%20the%20groundwork%20for%20it%20before%20the%20executive%20action%20targeting%20Perkins%20Coie%20came%20down%20on%20March%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20changes%20underway%20in%20the%20new%20administration%20focused%20on%20procurement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Vinson%20%26amp%3B%20Elkins%20%26quot%3Bsaw%20me%20as%20someone%20who%20could%20come%20in%20and%20help%20really%20grow%20and%20expand%20on%20certain%20areas%20that%20are%20aligned%20with%20what%20the%20firm%20is%20trying%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%2C%20a%20White%20House%20office%20linked%20to%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20has%20pressed%20federal%20agencies%20to%20end%20contracts%20and%20slash%