20April%202.%3Cp%3ECarlos%20Barria%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOwner-operated%20businesses%20across%20states%20sued%20Trump%2C%20calling%20his%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20%26quot%3Billegal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lawsuit%20says%20Trump's%20tariffs%20violate%20constitutional%20limits%20on%20executive%20power.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20broadest%20lawsuits%20against%20Trump's%20tariffs%20yet.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-dynamic-pricing-inflation-costs-china-trade-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20facing%20increasing%20legal%20pushback%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20this%20time%20from%20five%20owner-operated%20businesses%20across%20different%20states%20and%20trades%2C%20from%20fishing%20gear%20to%20wine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Liberty%20Justice%20Center%2C%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20small%20businesses%2C%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20in%20the%20US%20Court%20of%20International%20Trade%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eon%20Monday%20challenging%20Trump's%20authority%20to%20impose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-online-reads-sound-smarter-about-trump-tariffs-canada-mexico-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20invoking%20the%20International%20Emergency%20Economic%20Powers%20Act%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20move%20violates%20constitutional%20limits%20on%20executive%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20states%20that%20Trump%20claimed%20the%20authority%20to%20%26quot%3Bunilaterally%20levy%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20on%20imports%2C%20%26quot%3Bcalculated%20via%20any%20methodology%20%E2%80%94%20or%20mere%20caprice%2C%26quot%3B%20without%20notice%20or%20public%20comment%20%26quot%3Bdespite%20massive%20economic%20impacts%20that%20are%20likely%20to%20do%20severe%20damage%20to%20the%20global%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20Court%20should%20declare%20the%20President's%20unprecedented%20power%20grab%20illegal%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20involves%20a%20wide%20scope%20of%20trades%20with%20businesses%20dealings%20in%2038%20countries%2C%20including%20a%20wine%20importer%20in%20New%20York%2C%20an%20online%20fishing%20gear%20company%2C%20a%20toy%20kit%20maker%2C%20a%20plumbing%20manufacturer%20in%20Utah%2C%20and%20a%20women's%20cycling%20apparel%20brand%20in%20Vermont.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20libertarian%20legal%20group%20is%20bringing%20the%20lawsuit%20against%20Trump%2C%20Secretary%20of%20Commerce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhoward-lutnick-social-security-check-missing-fraud-doge-cuts-ssa-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHoward%20Lutnick%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanceled-plans-to-visit-the-us-european-dont-feel-safe-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECustoms%20and%20Border%20Protection%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Acting%20Commissioner%20Peter%20R.%20Flores%2C%20and%20Trade%20Representative%20Jamieson%20Greer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20marks%20the%20third%20widely-known%20legal%20case%20aiming%20to%20undo%20Trump's%20tariffs%2C%20and%20perhaps%20the%20broadest.%20Members%20of%20the%20Blackfeet%20Nation%20have%20previously%20sued%20over%20Trump's%20Canada%20tariffs%2C%20and%20a%20small%20women-owned%20business%20in%20Florida%20has%20an%20ongoing%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-women-owned-business-florida-lawsuit-sues-trump-china-tariffs-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariffs%20on%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20similar%20constitutional%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20April%202%20tariff%20announcement%20set%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpresident-donald-trump-teases-exceptions-