%20me%20once%20I%20discovered%20that%20it's%20built%20to%20withstand%20any%20potential%20thefts%2C%20too.%20And%20the%20fact%20that%20it's%20under%20%2430%3F%20Cut%20to%20me%20immediately%20adding%20it%20to%20my%20shopping%20cart%20and%20bringing%20it%20along%20on%20every%20single%20vacation%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f0a12019-de7d-4ec8-9530-6e442025dd0d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%20and%20specs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%20and%20specs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20view%20of%20the%20pincnel%20backpack%20showing%20the%20zipper%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fd5dfec6ad288d147e1d6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhat%20makes%20the%20backpack%20%26quot%3Banti-theft%26quot%3B%20is%20that%20the%20main%20compartment%20is%20accessed%20by%20zippers%20hidden%20in%20the%20part%20of%20the%20backpack%20that%20usually%20sits%20flush%20against%20your%20body.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Sanders%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pincnel%20Anti-Theft%20Backpack%20has%20a%20small%20but%20mighty%20design%20that's%20packed%20with%20impressive%20features.%20My%20favorite%20is%20the%20zipper%20closures%2C%20which%20are%20designed%20to%20lay%20flat%20against%20your%20back%20instead%20of%20outside%20the%20bag%2C%20ensuring%20no%20one%20can%20easily%20unzip%20it%20and%20make%20off%20with%20your%20precious%20items.%20I%20really%20appreciate%20that%20the%20zippers%20aren't%20even%20visible%20once%20the%20bag%20is%20on%20your%20back.%20The%20zipper%20pulls%20are%20crafted%20from%20durable%20metal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20backpack%20is%20crafted%20in%20soft%2C%20shiny%2C%20water-resistant%20nylon.%20I've%20tested%20it%20in%20spring%20and%20summer%20rainstorms%2C%20and%20it%20adequately%20protected%20my%20items%20and%20remained%20looking%20brand%20new.%20The%20two%20shoulder%20straps%20%E2%80%94%20a%20combination%20of%20webbed%20nylon%20and%20luxe%20faux%20leather%20%E2%80%94%20are%20fully%20adjustable%20and%20work%20well%20for%20my%20shorter%20five-foot%20frame.%20The%20backpack%20gets%20a%20fashionable%20look%2C%20too%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20faux%20leather%20strip%20running%20down%20the%20center%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20backpack%20looks%20small%2C%20it's%20surprisingly%20mighty%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20holding%20travel%20essentials.%20The%20back%20compartment%20unzips%20to%20reveal%20a%20large%20pocket%20and%20two%20additional%20patch%20pockets.%20I%20like%20to%20use%20the%20patch%20pockets%20for%20items%20like%20my%20phone%2C%20lip%20balm%2C%20headphones%2C%20card%20case%2C%20and%20keys.%20In%20the%20larger%20pocket%2C%20I%20store%20a%20sweatshirt%2C%20phone%20charger%2C%20my%20iPad%2C%20cables%2C%20sunglasses%20case%2C%20and%20a%20pouch%20with%20beauty%20products.%20I've%20even%20fit%20an%20extra%20pair%20of%20shoes%20in%20it%20for%20a%20long%20day%20at%20Disneyland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20love%20that%20the%20exterior%20includes%20four%20additional%20pockets.%20Each%20side%20has%20one%20pouch%20pocket%20and%20one%20zippered%20welt%20pocket%2C%20which%20are%20large%20enough%20to%20hold%20a%20water%20bottle%2C%20phone%2C%20sunscreen%2C%20wallet%2C%20mints%2C%20and%20earbuds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e9c50001-622b-4150-a844-9198276c00a8%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20it's%20like%20to%20use%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it's%20like%20to%20use%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Backpack%20shown%20with%20its%20contents%20arranged%20around%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fd5e68c6ad288d147e1d7b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20backpack%20can%20hold%20all%20the%20essentials%20for%20a%20long%20flight%20or%20a%20day%20of%20exploration.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Sanders%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3