edia.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1744380932-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-419765%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Timber%20Residence%20in%20Vagator%2C%20Goa%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20first%20residences%20in%20India%20built%20using%20glulam.%20Picture%20source%3A%20Akshat%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CCompared%20to%20materials%20like%20concrete%20and%20steel%2C%20which%20release%20carbon%20during%20their%20production%2C%20mass%20timber%20sequesters%20it%2C%20making%20the%20material%20carbon-negative%20and%20a%20sustainable%20alternative%2C%E2%80%9D%20Akshat%20points%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20architects%20can%20render%20fire%20and%20moisture-resistant%20properties%20to%20the%20material%20by%20treating%20it.%20Akshat%20has%20always%20admired%20glulam%E2%80%99s%20versatility%3B%20being%20prefabricated%2C%20it%20allows%20swift%20assembly.%20Homes%20that%20shy%20away%20from%20maximalism%2C%20while%20not%20wanting%20to%20compromise%20on%20aesthetics%2C%20could%20give%20glulam%20a%20try.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20not%20just%20concrete%2C%20it%20could%20well%20substitute%20steel%20too.%20A%20study%20reported%20that%20glulam%20%E2%80%9Chas%20a%20smaller%20tendency%20to%20lateral%20torsional%20buckling%20than%20steel%20beams%20and%20that%20they%20can%20be%20cheaper%20and%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386103%2Fsustainable-architecture-in-india-green-pavers-cseb-earth-blocks-orient-stranded-boar