nment%20and%20farmers%20that%20have%20benefited.%20The%20project%20has%20created%20employment%20opportunities%20for%20the%20local%20community%2C%20with%2024%20people%20now%20working%20at%20the%20processing%20plant%20and%20hundreds%20of%20them%20helping%20collect%20weeds%20at%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Adil%2C%20the%20site%20manager%20at%20CEF%20Group%20overseeing%20the%20scientific%20processing%20plant%20at%20CEF%20Srinagar%20Biofuel%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CCEF%20Group%E2%80%99s%20innovative%20waste%20processing%20plant%20has%20a%20capacity%20of%20140%20tonnes%20per%20day.%20By%20removing%20waste%20from%20Dal%20Lake%2C%20it%20directly%20improves%20water%20quality%2C%20restores%20biodiversity%2C%20and%20enhances%20the%20lake%E2%80%99s%20natural%20beauty.%20This%20has%20had%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20reviving%20tourism%20and%20boosting%20local%20businesses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20has%20also%20brought%20social%20benefits%2C%20creating%20over%201%2C500%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20particularly%20for%20local%20youth.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20these%20workers%20assist%20in%20collecting%20lake%20weeds%2C%20while%20others%20contribute%20directly%20to%20the%20operation%20of%20the%20plant%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adil%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20a%20win-win%20for%20all%20of%20us%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20community%E2%80%99s%20response%20has%20been%20positive%2C%20even%20though%20they%20were%20initially%20hesitant%20regarding%20the%20odour%20and%20pollution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maninder%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20created%20jobs%2C%20improved%20the%20local%20environment%2C%20and%20provided%20farmers%20with%20affordable%20and%20rich%20manure.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20win-win%20for%20all%20of%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20to%20the%20future%2C%20he%20aims%20to%20replicate%20this%20success%20in%20other%20Indian%20lakes%20%E2%80%94%20